snippet.title: Amber Heard-The Lengths Narcissists Will Go When They're Caught!
snippet.description:
This is just a quick weigh-in on the never-ending saga on Johnny Depp and Amber Heard, and the lengths SHE goes to to cover her arse.
Check out Incredibly Average's latest video about how Amber Heard admitted to multiple acts of violence against Johnny Depp!
https://www.youtube.com/watch?time_continue=3&v=PbXTr41ZFTQ

Email me at jyenkotah@keeptruthalive.org if you have any questions.
I am NOT being paid by Johnny Depp to make these videos.  That is a hilarious accusation we who have defended Johnny for three years have gotten repeatedly. 
I speak out on what I believe in, and this situation is very important to me because I've experienced a version of narcissistic abuse and gaslighting similar to what Johnny Depp experienced at this woman's hands.
I will always stand by Johnny Depp and other narcissistic abuse survivors.  Keep Soldiering On!!!!
